The first step in the review and selection process is an administrative review to determine eligibility and appropriateness.
For each Center, the following evaluation criteria will be used to evaluate pre-proposals: 

 Short- and long-term benefits to the Minority Academic Institution; 

 Benefits to principal investigator professional development; 

